metadata.name: "A New Rising Sun" 1 of 10 series
metadata.description:
Join me in my new artistic journey and become a "Experienced" Hendrix collector of this series. 

Jimi Hendrix was my first muse. His music runs in my blood, his message of freedom and love still sounding clear. 
I've painted Hendrix 100s of times, but this is the first digital NFT.

This NFT is more than the digital art, it includes a frame-able 12inx18in canvas giclee print, numbered and signed which will be ready for a frame and shipped.

Collectors will be first to be notified of all future drops in the series. There will be a new one dropped once a week. 
Once the series of 10 are all sold a new image of Jimi Hendrix will be used to create from and this specific image will never be used or sold again.
